"title": "8367: wisdom, importance of human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8367",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>True wisdom may bring material reward but its value far exceeds earthly riches. To those who receive it, it opens a path to life and security and equips for leadership and right conduct.</p>\n<h2>The supreme value of true wisdom</h2>\n<h3>It is priceless</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:7\">PRO 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13\">PRO 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:10-Prov8:11\">PRO 8:10–8:11</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:24\">PRO 15:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:30\">PRO 11:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:14\">PRO 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:22\">PRO 16:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:14\">PRO 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a></p>\n<h3>It brings prosperity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:18\">PRO 8:18</a></strong> <em>The benefits of wisdom may include material prosperity, but more important is the moral and spiritual prosperity which it brings.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:1-Prov3:2\">PRO 3:1–3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:8\">PRO 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:8\">PRO 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:20-Prov21:21\">PRO 21:20–21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:3\">PRO 24:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:21\">JER 10:21</a></p>\n<h3>It gives security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:6\">PRO 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:33\">PRO 1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:6-Prov2:11\">PRO 2:6–2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:3\">PRO 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:26\">PRO 28:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:5\">ECC 8:5</a></p>\n<h2>The application of wisdom</h2>\n<h3>It touches the whole person</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:12\">1KI 3:12</a></strong> <em>In Hebrew, the “heart” represents the centre of human personality.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:36\">JOB 38:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:6\">PSA 51:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:2\">PRO 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:23\">PRO 16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:17\">PRO 22:17</a></p>\n<h3>It results in right action</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:5\">COL 4:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13\">JAS 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:34\">PSA 119:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:3\">PRO 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:11\">PRO 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:21\">PRO 15:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:19\">PRO 23:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:19\">ROM 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:15\">EPH 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9-Col1:10\">COL 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:14-Jas3:17\">JAS 3:14–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>It results in watchfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:1-Matt25:10\">MAT 25:1–25:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:8\">PRO 14:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:3\">PRO 22:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:12\">PRO 27:12</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom is necessary for leaders</h2>\n<h3>Wisdom to govern</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:15-Prov8:16\">PRO 8:15–8:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3\">ACT 6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:13\">DEU 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:7\">1KI 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:12\">1CH 22:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:10\">PSA 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:22\">PSA 105:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:2\">PRO 28:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:16\">ECC 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:11\">ISA 56:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:15\">JER 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom to administer justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:28\">1KI 3:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:9\">1KI 3:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:10\">2CH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:30\">PSA 37:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:26\">PRO 20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:23\">PRO 24:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:45\">MAT 24:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:42\">LUK 12:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:5\">1CO 6:5</a></p>\n<h2>The teaching of wisdom</h2>\n<h3>The wise give instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:9\">ECC 12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:30\">PSA 37:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:3\">PSA 49:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:20-Prov1:21\">PRO 1:20–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:1\">PRO 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:1\">PRO 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:21\">PRO 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:26\">PRO 31:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:33\">DAN 11:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:6-1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>The wise listen to instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:5\">PRO 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:31\">PRO 15:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:1\">PRO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:9\">PRO 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:8\">PRO 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:20\">PRO 13:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:12\">PRO 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:20\">PRO 19:20</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those endowed with wisdom</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:10\">ACT 7:10</a> <em>Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:15\">DEU 1:15</a> <em>the elders of Israel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a> <em>Joshua</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:20\">2SA 14:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:72\">PSA 78:72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:16-1Kgs3:28\">1KI 3:16–3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29-1Kgs4:34\">1KI 4:29–4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:4-1Kgs10:8\">1KI 10:4–10:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:3-2Chr9:7\">2CH 9:3–9:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:12-1Chr22:13\">1CH 22:12–22:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:42\">MAT 12:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:31\">LUK 11:31</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:25\">EZR 7:25</a> <em>Ezra</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a> <em>the Messiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:17\">DAN 1:17</a> <em>Daniel and his three friends</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:19-Dan2:23\">DAN 2:19–2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:27-Dan2:28\">DAN 2:27–2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11-Dan5:12\">DAN 5:11–5:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:15\">2PE 3:15</a> <em>Paul</em></p>",
